result.name: ID causal variation in Malinois with SAMS
result.description: Identification of causal variation in Malinois dogs affected by spinocerebellar ataxia (most important feature), paraparesis and myokymia-like muscle contractions. This variant is also available via the OMIA database https://omia.org/OMIA002279/9615/
result.center: LDG, Faculty of Veterinary Sciences, Ghent University
